When using 'Look' in vocalize menu, print corresponding item to chat area and make item glow or mark the area like back 4 blood.

-ChangeLog-
v0.6
-Add all gun weapons, melee weapons, minigun, ammo and items.
-Add cooldown.
-Add Glow, everyone can see the item through wall.
-Add Mark, using 'Look' in vocalize menu to mark the area.

v0.2
-Original Post: https://forums.alliedmods.net/showthread.php?t=333669

-Convars-
cfg\sourcemod\l4d2_item_hint.cfg
// Cold Down Time in seconds a player can use 'Look' item/mark hint again.
l4d2_item_hint_cooldown_time "2.5"

// Item Glow Color, Three values between 0-255 separated by spaces. (Empty = Disable Glow)
l4d2_item_hint_glow_color "0 255 255"

// Item Glow Range.
l4d2_item_hint_glow_range "1000"

// Item Glow Time.
l4d2_item_hint_glow_timer "15.0"

// How close can a player use 'Look' item hint.
l4d2_item_hint_use_range "150"

// Item Hint Sound. (Empty = OFF)
l4d2_item_hint_use_sound "buttons/blip1.wav"

// Mark Glow Color, Three values between 0-255 separated by spaces. (Empty = Disable Glow)
l4d2_mark_hint_glow_color "200 200 200"

// Mark Glow Time.
l4d2_mark_hint_glow_timer "10.0"

// How far away can a player use 'Look' mark hint.
l4d2_mark_hint_use_range "900"

// Mark Hint Sound. (Empty = OFF)
l4d2_mark_hint_use_sound "buttons/blip1.wav"

-Commands-
None
